ization: Bearer <token>`.\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-15-- Datas sûÈo serializadas em ISO 8601.\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-16-- Enums sûÈo serializados como string.\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-17-\r\n--\ndocs\\api-reference.md-67-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-68----\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-69-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-70-## Cliente\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-71-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-72-### Registrar novo cliente\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-73-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-74-```text\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md:75:POST /api/v1/cliente\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-76-```\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-77-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-78-```jsonc\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-79-// Request\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-80-{\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-81-  \"cpf\": \"12345678901\",\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-82-  \"nome\": \"Fulano de Tal\",\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-83-  \"dataNascimento\": \"1990-01-31\",\r\n--\ndocs\\api-reference.md-107-    \"clienteId\": 9999\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-108-  }\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-109-}\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-110-```\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-111-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-112-### Consultar cliente pelo ID\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-113-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-114-```text\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md:115:GET /api/v1/cliente/{clienteId}\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-116-```\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-117-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-118-```jsonc\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-119-// Response - 200 OK\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-120-{\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-121-  \"status\": true,\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-122-  \"message\": \"\",\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-123-  \"data\": {\r\n--\ndocs\\api-reference.md-142-    }\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-143-  }\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-144-}\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-145-```\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-146-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-147-### Consultar cliente pelo CPF\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-148-\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-149-```text\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md:150:GET /api/v1/cliente/cpf/{cpf}\r\ndocs\\api-reference.md-151-```\r\ndo